						a(href="#legal") Legal
			.container.columns.small-12.medium-8.large-9
				.row#branding-assets.padding-b-2: .columns
					h1 Branding Assets
					p: strong Hello Ackleners! 
					p We want to improve your use of our brand. Which is why we provide these Acklen Avenue branding resources. Use them wisely whenever you need them. You will find each asset individually in this section. You can also download all of them together by clicking here:
					a(class="button" href="resources/Branding-assets.zip") Download branding assets
				
				hr(class="divider--secondary" aria-label="hidden")
				
				.row: .columns
					h2 The Logo
					p Use the Acklen Avenue Logo in 4 color versions:
					p: small If you want to know more about the correct use of the logo go to our 
						a(href="#branding-guidelines") Branding Guidelines
					
					.row.padding-b-2
						.columns.small-12.medium-6
							figure.branding-assets__item
								img(src="resources/Branding/AA-Logo/Vector/AA-Logo-AppleGreen.svg")
								figcaption Apple Green Version in 
									a(href="resources/Branding/AA-Logo/Vector/AA-Logo-AppleGreen.svg" download) SVG 
									| or 
									a(href="resources/Branding/AA-Logo/PNG/AA-Logo-AppleGreen-regular.png" download) PNG
						.columns.small-12.medium-6
							figure.branding-assets__item
								img(src="resources/Branding/AA-Logo/Vector/AA-Logo-SlatePurple.svg")
								figcaption Slate Purple Version in 
									a(href="resources/Branding/AA-Logo/Vector/AA-Logo-Slatepurple.svg" download) SVG 
									| or 
									a(href="resources/Branding/AA-Logo/PNG/AA-Logo-SlatePurple-regular.png" download) PNG
						.columns.small-12.medium-6
							figure.branding-assets__item
								img(class="bg-secondary" src="resources/Branding/AA-Logo/Vector/AA-Logo-PaleGrey.svg")
								figcaption Pale Grey Version in 
									a(href="resources/Branding/AA-Logo/Vector/AA-Logo-PaleGrey.svg" download) SVG 
									| or 
									a(href="resources/Branding/AA-Logo/PNG/AA-Logo-PaleGrey-regular.png" download) PNG
						.columns.small-12.medium-6
							figure.branding-assets__item
								img(class="bg-secondary" src="resources/Branding/AA-Logo/Vector/AA-Logo-White.svg")
								figcaption White Version in 
									a(href="resources/Branding/AA-Logo/Vector/AA-Logo-White.svg" download) SVG 
									| or 
									a(href="resources/Branding/AA-Logo/PNG/AA-Logo-White-regular.png" download) PNG
				
				hr(class="divider--secondary" aria-label="hidden")
				
				.row: .columns
					h2 Acklen Heart
					p The Acklen Heart is a symbolic element. We avoid using it inside at the same time of our logo. Think on it as a decorative element.

					.row.padding-b-2
						.columns.large-6
							figure.branding-assets__item
								img(src="resources/Branding/Acklen-Heart/Vector/acklen-heart.svg")
								figcaption Download our Acklen Heart in 
									a(href="resources/Branding/Acklen-Heart/Vector/acklen-heart.svg" download) SVG 
									| or 
									a(href="resources/Branding/Acklen-Heart/PNG/acklen-heart-no-bg.png" download) PNG
				
				hr(class="divider--secondary" aria-label="hidden")
				
